enumerated candidate at `(bigN, cutoff)` is rejected by the checker. -/
theorem projectLengthTimeBoundCanonicalConjIntroTargetSearchFrontierMonomialSearchExtractor_full_trace_noFallback
    {scale_data : InternalPudlakTheorem5ScaleData}
    {L : _root_.FirstOrder.Language.{u, v}} {α : Type w} {n : Nat}
    {Ax : L.BoundedFormula α n → Prop}
    {A B : Nat → L.BoundedFormula α n}
